{
  "id": "adv_main_01_04_03",
  "title": "星見編1章19話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLE……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、そちらは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hi. Who might you be?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.486802744865418,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 2.4868027448654177
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？\nスタジオ間違えちゃった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\nWe’re in the wrong studio?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.790793697039288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "……星見プロダクション……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi Productions…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.9907936970392885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "星見……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.624127030372623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、はい。星見プロダクションの者です。実は\nこの子達は新人のアイドルで、これからレッスンを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ yes. We’re from Hoshimi Productions.\nThese are our newest idols. They’re here for their lesson.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.257460363705956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました\n長瀬麻奈さんが所属していた事務所ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I know‚\nYou’re from the agency Mana Nagase belonged to‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.057460363705967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんが設立したんですよね\n事務所で聞いたことあります。凄い方だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe Saegusa-san is the founder.\nI’ve heard about him at our agency. They say he’s a legend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.15746036370597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、凄いんですね\n三枝さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow! Saegusa-san\nis a legend…!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.25746036370597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……先輩には挨拶……\n……芸能界は上下関係が厳しい世界……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We should introduce ourselves…\nShowbiz has a strict hierarchy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.19079369703929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.67585054238638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "川咲さくらです。まだアイドル始めたばかりですけど\n追いつけるよう頑張ります。よろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m Sakura Kawasaki. I’ve just started out as an idol‚\nbut I’ll do my best to catch up to you. Nice meeting you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.44251720905305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん！\nダメだよぅ……追いつくなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura!\nYou can’t say things like “catch up.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.58371230947212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "あの人達はすっごい人気ある人達なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE is a super popular group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.90690204488472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……失礼……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s rude…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.90690204488472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？\nでも、やるからにはトップ目指して頑張らなきゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?\nI mean‚ if we’re gonna do this‚ we should aim for the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.60690204488471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "それはあくまで私達の中ではの話で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s the type of talk we should keep between ourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.37356871155139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "フフフ……構わないですよ\nそのくらいの気持ちがないと。ね？　優",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heheh… Don’t worry about it.\nYou need that level of determination. Isn’t that right‚ Yu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.62241231786446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sure do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.35574565119778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね、私達のスタジオは隣だったみたい\n瑠依ちゃん、行こう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry about the mix up. Looks like our studio was next door.\nLet’s go‚ Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.69892027564084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "待って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.23225360897418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（――瑠依の微笑を見た二人は）\n（それだけで彼女が何をしたいかを理解したようだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Seeing Rui’s smile‚）\n（the two others seem to guess what she has in mind.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.83225360897417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、ええけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine by me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.19892027564084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tri-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 92.8313465375427
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（三人は並ぶと、瑠依の合図でステップを踏み始めた）\n（動きの速さ、滑らかさ、どれをとっても素晴らしい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The three line up and begin dancing on Rui’s cue.）\n（The speed and fluidity of their steps are incredible.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.05681140608822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（しかも、息一つ乱れない）\n（激しい動きにもかかわらず、平静を保ったままだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And not a breath out of place.）\n（They remain perfectly calm despite their intense movements.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0034329830332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（俺も、さくらも、みんなも、ただ圧倒されていた）\n（息を止めて、見守っていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sakura‚ myself‚ and the rest of the group are rendered speechless.）\n（We hold our breath and take it all in.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.52009984043478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "…………ご静聴ありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you for watching.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ by the way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.87390494532625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリで\n戦えるといいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope we get to compete\nat the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1136.1271241032823,
          "startTime": 123.13612712410328
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 125.03612712410332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
